## Development Workflow

### Branch Structure
- `main` - Production code
- `qa/staging` - QA environment
- `dev/main` - Development main branch
- `dev/feature-name` - Feature branches

### Making Changes
1. Create feature branch from `dev/main`
2. Make your changes
3. Create PR to `dev/main`
4. After review, merge to `dev/main`
5. Deploy to QA via `qa/staging`
6. Deploy to production via `main`

